1
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:23,410
♪The autumn wind slips in,
never asking when I'll return♪

2
00:00:24,480 --> 00:00:27,170
♪Before the mirror,
I comb my hair, lips parted just so♪

3
00:00:28,270 --> 00:00:30,670
♪An old melody plays faintly,
perhaps the answer to this life♪

4
00:00:30,670 --> 00:00:33,780
♪If fate leaves any trace at all♪

5
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,160
♪Wild geese disappear in the woods,
flowers wither at dusk♪

6
00:00:38,810 --> 00:00:41,780
♪How cruel the moonlight flooding
the empty tower, wine growing cold♪

7
00:00:42,140 --> 00:00:44,530
♪Long dreams and night rain
tearing through the heart of Luoyang♪

8
00:00:44,530 --> 00:00:48,380
♪Who still rides forth
to keep a vow long left behind?♪

9
00:00:49,480 --> 00:00:51,410
♪Paint the love and the hate♪

10
00:00:52,100 --> 00:00:55,040
♪With gentle strokes of ink,
like a lone wild goose flying far away♪

11
00:00:55,810 --> 00:00:57,960
♪Frost and snow to sketch memories,
drawn taut like a bow♪

12
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:59,550
♪One arrow dyed in deepest red♪

13
00:00:59,550 --> 00:01:03,230
♪The bitter chill within my heart♪

14
00:01:03,890 --> 00:01:06,520
♪The sorrow falling between your brows♪

15
00:01:06,520 --> 00:01:08,300
♪Scalding memories lodged in my throat♪

16
00:01:08,300 --> 00:01:11,290
♪Burning away the warmth we once shared♪

17
00:01:11,290 --> 00:01:13,800
♪I would fade away
with the candle's shadow♪

18
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:15,700
♪Sever the ties and stay behind alone♪

19
00:01:15,700 --> 00:01:18,340
♪Let you go♪

20
00:01:18,550 --> 00:01:21,240
♪Your sorrow lingers as you glance back♪

21
00:01:21,240 --> 00:01:23,150
♪This longing has already worn me thin♪

22
00:01:23,150 --> 00:01:26,460
♪We once vowed to grow old together♪

23
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:29,050
♪But if fate bears no guilt, then why♪

24
00:01:29,050 --> 00:01:33,460
♪Does it play this song of tears
for me alone?♪

25
00:01:34,340 --> 00:01:39,580
=Destiny of Love=
(Adapted from Lin Nan's novel, Destiny of Love.)

26
00:01:39,630 --> 00:01:42,400
=Episode 9=

27
00:01:56,500 --> 00:01:57,190
Bilian...

28
00:01:58,830 --> 00:02:00,030
The audacity of her!

29
00:02:06,030 --> 00:02:06,500
Bilian?

30
00:02:07,910 --> 00:02:09,270
Why are you back here?

31
00:02:09,510 --> 00:02:09,900
It's...

32
00:02:10,860 --> 00:02:11,580
It's nothing.

33
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:12,620
Wait a minute.

34
00:02:13,555 --> 00:02:14,200
Stay still!

35
00:02:14,266 --> 00:02:15,110
Stop right there!

36
00:02:16,550 --> 00:02:17,020
Bilian!

37
00:02:18,860 --> 00:02:19,300
Jiufeng.

38
00:02:19,740 --> 00:02:20,140
Jiufeng!

39
00:02:20,510 --> 00:02:21,110
Help!

40
00:02:21,510 --> 00:02:22,270
Help!

41
00:02:22,550 --> 00:02:24,420
Jiufeng...

42
00:02:39,755 --> 00:02:40,911
Your Highness.

43
00:02:42,688 --> 00:02:43,900
What are you panicking about?

44
00:02:46,266 --> 00:02:47,700
Bilian tried to poison Prince Jin.

45
00:02:48,050 --> 00:02:49,977
She then ran away
and went back to Noble Consort

46
00:02:49,977 --> 00:02:51,177
after getting caught red-handed.

47
00:02:52,790 --> 00:02:54,580
Well, is Princess Aliya hurt?

48
00:02:55,670 --> 00:02:57,020
She is all fine.

49
00:02:57,755 --> 00:02:58,755
That's great to hear.

50
00:02:59,740 --> 00:03:01,300
Deal with Bilian as soon as possible.

51
00:03:01,355 --> 00:03:03,066
After all, Brother won't let it slide.

52
00:03:07,140 --> 00:03:08,790
I feel so hot...

53
00:03:10,180 --> 00:03:11,350
It's hot...

54
00:03:22,230 --> 00:03:22,830
It's hot...

55
00:04:09,700 --> 00:04:11,700
Did I let him call me Manman last night?

56
00:04:14,270 --> 00:04:15,300
What do I do?

57
00:04:20,910 --> 00:04:21,380
Manman.

58
00:04:25,230 --> 00:04:25,910
You're awake.

59
00:04:28,844 --> 00:04:30,150
Who said you could call me that?

60
00:04:30,590 --> 00:04:31,260
Only my father...

61
00:04:32,420 --> 00:04:35,500
Only my parents can call me that.

62
00:04:37,550 --> 00:04:37,990
Fine.

63
00:04:38,740 --> 00:04:41,030
Freshen up and have your breakfast, Aliya.

64
00:04:51,111 --> 00:04:52,955
That was close.
I almost gave myself away.

65
00:04:53,777 --> 00:04:55,030
I'm as quick-witted as ever.

66
00:04:58,264 --> 00:05:00,720
(Benevolent and Kind)

67
00:05:00,790 --> 00:05:01,470
Yuetao. Jiufeng.

68
00:05:01,710 --> 00:05:02,470
Are you alright?

69
00:05:04,910 --> 00:05:05,910
We're all fine.

70
00:05:06,620 --> 00:05:08,380
But she dared try to poison

71
00:05:08,420 --> 00:05:09,590
you two!

72
00:05:10,060 --> 00:05:11,230
She's truly unbelievable!

73
00:05:11,940 --> 00:05:13,030
Even so,

74
00:05:13,350 --> 00:05:14,740
Bilian works for Noble Consort.

75
00:05:15,066 --> 00:05:16,666
And she came here following the decree.

76
00:05:17,110 --> 00:05:18,670
Is there anything we can do about her?

77
00:05:19,710 --> 00:05:21,300
The easiest way

78
00:05:21,710 --> 00:05:24,420
is Aliya and I seek
an explanation from Noble Consort.

79
00:05:26,311 --> 00:05:27,755
Do I have to be there too?

80
00:05:27,755 --> 00:05:30,490
(Hanyuan Hall)

81
00:05:31,180 --> 00:05:31,910
Physician Bilian,

82
00:05:32,380 --> 00:05:33,500
how dare you!

83
00:05:34,590 --> 00:05:35,470
I didn't expect you

84
00:05:35,888 --> 00:05:37,866
to cause trouble
at Prince Jin's Residence.

85
00:05:38,350 --> 00:05:38,910
Your Majesty.

86
00:05:39,710 --> 00:05:40,710
Bilian

87
00:05:40,790 --> 00:05:42,710
doesn't look like that kind of person.

88
00:05:43,300 --> 00:05:45,790
Besides, she's a reputable figure
at the Imperial Hospital.

89
00:05:46,620 --> 00:05:49,470
Prince Jin and Princess Consort Jin
might have misunderstood her.

90
00:05:50,150 --> 00:05:51,110
Father,

91
00:05:51,933 --> 00:05:53,288
I am telling the truth.

92
00:05:55,940 --> 00:05:56,380
Bilian.

93
00:05:57,620 --> 00:05:59,300
You were recommended by Noble Consort.

94
00:06:00,350 --> 00:06:02,790
However, you've committed
such a grave crime!

95
00:06:02,911 --> 00:06:03,470
Your Majesty!

96
00:06:03,820 --> 00:06:05,940
I did that because I
was left with no choice!

97
00:06:06,622 --> 00:06:08,133
You were left with no choice?

98
00:06:08,955 --> 00:06:10,790
I've worked
for Imperial Hospital for years.

99
00:06:11,380 --> 00:06:12,940
I wouldn't say I'm skilled,

100
00:06:13,470 --> 00:06:14,670
but I remain professional

101
00:06:14,822 --> 00:06:16,955
when it comes
to treatments and prescriptions.

102
00:06:17,300 --> 00:06:20,710
And that is the reason
why Her Highness cannot accept me.

103
00:06:22,066 --> 00:06:22,860
What do you mean?

104
00:06:24,180 --> 00:06:24,740
Your Majesty.

105
00:06:24,888 --> 00:06:26,590
Her Highness knows nothing
about medicine.

106
00:06:26,688 --> 00:06:28,644
The method she used
to treat His Highness's legs

107
00:06:28,644 --> 00:06:30,155
was worse than those of charlatans.

108
00:06:31,230 --> 00:06:32,620
If I'm not mistaken,

109
00:06:33,260 --> 00:06:35,180
Princess Consort Jin is a fake!

110
00:06:40,420 --> 00:06:40,990
This woman

111
00:06:41,380 --> 00:06:43,030
is definitely not the Princess of Xilin!

112
00:06:44,060 --> 00:06:44,590
Bilian.

113
00:06:45,990 --> 00:06:46,683
Are you aware

114
00:06:46,684 --> 00:06:49,000
accusing an imperial family member
is a great crime?

115
00:06:49,150 --> 00:06:49,710
I dare not!

116
00:06:49,710 --> 00:06:51,470
Please exercise your judgment,
Your Majesty.

117
00:06:51,470 --> 00:06:52,260
Everyone knows

118
00:06:52,333 --> 00:06:54,670
the Princess of Xilin
is the best physician in the world.

119
00:06:55,420 --> 00:06:56,670
But from my recent observation,

120
00:06:57,230 --> 00:06:59,150
this woman knows nothing about medicine.

121
00:06:59,910 --> 00:07:00,500
That proves

122
00:07:00,790 --> 00:07:01,990
she's an impostor.

123
00:07:02,555 --> 00:07:03,420
(Well done, Bilian.)

124
00:07:03,555 --> 00:07:04,300
(Keep going.)

125
00:07:05,150 --> 00:07:06,420
(His Majesty favors Prince Jin.)

126
00:07:06,500 --> 00:07:07,860
(Just say what I told you.)

127
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,910
(It doesn't matter
whether she's a fake or not.)

128
00:07:09,910 --> 00:07:12,180
(If she can't cure his legs,
she will be executed.)

129
00:07:12,590 --> 00:07:13,990
(When Xilin gets upset about it,)

130
00:07:14,150 --> 00:07:15,670
(Prince Jin will be implicated.)

131
00:07:15,670 --> 00:07:17,380
(There will be no way
turning back for him.)

132
00:07:17,380 --> 00:07:17,740
Father.

133
00:07:18,940 --> 00:07:20,380
Aliya is my wife.

134
00:07:21,060 --> 00:07:23,030
She is also the one treating my legs.

135
00:07:23,990 --> 00:07:26,180
My legs are already showing
signs of improvement.

136
00:07:26,466 --> 00:07:27,740
She is truly a divine physician.

137
00:07:27,822 --> 00:07:28,777
That cannot be faked.

138
00:07:29,022 --> 00:07:30,670
Please look into this thoroughly, Father.

139
00:07:32,044 --> 00:07:33,844
That is precisely the problem,
Your Highness.

140
00:07:34,260 --> 00:07:36,350
Because she is your wife,

141
00:07:36,820 --> 00:07:38,550
you should all the more avoid suspicion.

142
00:07:42,844 --> 00:07:44,590
Your Majesty,
please exercise your judgment.

143
00:07:44,590 --> 00:07:45,910
I, Bilian, swear on my life

144
00:07:45,977 --> 00:07:48,380
Princess Consort Jin
is definitely not the Princess of Xilin.

145
00:07:49,977 --> 00:07:51,088
Princess Consort Jin,

146
00:07:51,088 --> 00:07:52,511
do you have anything to say?

147
00:07:53,022 --> 00:07:53,600
I...

148
00:07:56,380 --> 00:07:56,740
Father,

149
00:07:57,550 --> 00:07:59,110
she is obviously framing me.

150
00:08:01,300 --> 00:08:01,620
Bilian,

151
00:08:02,470 --> 00:08:04,420
do you have any evidence
to back your claim?

152
00:08:04,990 --> 00:08:05,230
I...

153
00:08:06,820 --> 00:08:07,230
Enough.

154
00:08:08,066 --> 00:08:09,470
Whether she is genuine or not,

155
00:08:10,030 --> 00:08:11,230
we will find out right away.

156
00:08:12,260 --> 00:08:12,590
Here.

157
00:08:13,555 --> 00:08:14,910
Summon Imperial Physician Liu.

158
00:08:14,910 --> 00:08:15,688
Yes, Your Majesty.

159
00:08:22,790 --> 00:08:23,550
Take Bilian away.

160
00:08:24,110 --> 00:08:25,110
Once I get to the truth,

161
00:08:25,422 --> 00:08:26,470
I'll make my decision.

162
00:08:32,627 --> 00:08:34,700
(Hanyuan Hall)

163
00:08:34,740 --> 00:08:36,860
Imperial Physician Liu is here.

164
00:08:43,070 --> 00:08:43,660
Your Majesty,

165
00:08:44,020 --> 00:08:46,780
to ensure fairness in this test,

166
00:08:47,230 --> 00:08:50,780
I picked several commoners
from the market

167
00:08:51,310 --> 00:08:53,110
to come with me to the palace.

168
00:08:54,140 --> 00:08:55,350
How thoughtful of you.

169
00:08:57,470 --> 00:08:58,070
Her Highness,

170
00:08:58,470 --> 00:09:00,740
acupoints, prescriptions,
and pulse-taking

171
00:09:01,230 --> 00:09:04,310
are the basics
of diagnosing and treating illnesses.

172
00:09:04,660 --> 00:09:06,470
Let's begin the first round,

173
00:09:06,577 --> 00:09:07,990
acupuncture point identification.

174
00:09:08,500 --> 00:09:08,950
Please.

175
00:09:25,740 --> 00:09:27,950
(I did learn acupuncture from Aliya,)

176
00:09:28,666 --> 00:09:30,266
(but there are so many acupoints...)

177
00:09:30,470 --> 00:09:31,990
(And the techniques are precise.)

178
00:09:32,590 --> 00:09:34,070
(With my shallow skills,)

179
00:09:34,350 --> 00:09:35,540
(if I actually give it a try,)

180
00:09:36,070 --> 00:09:37,660
(I will definitely be exposed.)

181
00:09:40,260 --> 00:09:43,110
Your Highness, please apply acupuncture
to Fengchi Point.

182
00:09:44,900 --> 00:09:46,710
(Fengchi Point...)

183
00:09:48,380 --> 00:09:50,430
(I think Aliya once mentioned it.)

184
00:09:50,740 --> 00:09:52,950
(Fengchi is about two fingers wide
behind the ear.)

185
00:09:55,500 --> 00:09:56,780
(However...)

186
00:09:57,500 --> 00:09:58,950
(What if they ask me )

187
00:09:59,380 --> 00:10:01,620
(to do more acupoints after this one?)

188
00:10:03,620 --> 00:10:05,590
(I might as well give up now.)

189
00:10:07,044 --> 00:10:07,990
I'm not doing it.

190
00:10:11,950 --> 00:10:12,860
Why not?

191
00:10:15,710 --> 00:10:16,110
Father,

192
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:18,230
it's because he is not sick at all.

193
00:10:18,780 --> 00:10:19,260
Look at him.

194
00:10:19,990 --> 00:10:20,710
This man

195
00:10:21,140 --> 00:10:23,900
is as strong as an ox,
and he has a healthy complexion.

196
00:10:24,590 --> 00:10:26,590
He looks full of life.

197
00:10:27,020 --> 00:10:28,140
So he is not sick at all.

198
00:10:28,422 --> 00:10:30,070
As a physician, I must be compassionate.

199
00:10:30,430 --> 00:10:31,711
How could I perform acupuncture

200
00:10:31,733 --> 00:10:33,377
on someone who is not even sick?

201
00:10:34,088 --> 00:10:35,733
Imperial Physician Liu, am I right?

202
00:10:37,070 --> 00:10:39,230
What Your Highness said makes sense.

203
00:10:41,660 --> 00:10:42,260
(My goodness.)

204
00:10:43,260 --> 00:10:44,260
She's the one who's sick.

205
00:10:51,620 --> 00:10:52,310
Your Highness,

206
00:10:52,860 --> 00:10:54,780
the second round
is a test on prescriptions.

207
00:10:56,070 --> 00:10:57,900
This child is only four years old

208
00:10:58,430 --> 00:11:00,430
and has merely caught a cold.

209
00:11:01,020 --> 00:11:03,740
Please prescribe a remedy accordingly.

210
00:11:30,310 --> 00:11:31,230
(Got it.)

211
00:11:44,866 --> 00:11:45,780
Imperial Physician Liu.

212
00:11:47,400 --> 00:11:48,310
Please take a look.

213
00:12:02,780 --> 00:12:03,350
Your Majesty,

214
00:12:04,190 --> 00:12:05,620
forgive me, but my knowledge is poor.

215
00:12:06,260 --> 00:12:07,500
I do not recognize

216
00:12:07,900 --> 00:12:10,260
the script on this paper.

217
00:12:12,780 --> 00:12:15,140
That's not surprising at all.

218
00:12:15,377 --> 00:12:17,400
This is a secret prescription from Xilin.

219
00:12:17,620 --> 00:12:19,900
Naturally, outsiders wouldn't
understand it.

220
00:12:20,310 --> 00:12:20,900
That's normal.

221
00:12:33,500 --> 00:12:35,350
(How would I know how to take a pulse?)

222
00:12:35,740 --> 00:12:37,990
(Her pulse feels different from normal,)

223
00:12:38,310 --> 00:12:39,740
(but the problem is...)

224
00:12:41,070 --> 00:12:42,350
I can't feel anything...

225
00:12:42,830 --> 00:12:43,950
(Feel nothing?)

226
00:12:45,222 --> 00:12:46,755
What's the matter with my child?

227
00:12:47,310 --> 00:12:48,190
(Child?)

228
00:12:48,830 --> 00:12:50,350
(She's pregnant?)

229
00:12:50,555 --> 00:12:51,190
Don't worry.

230
00:12:51,660 --> 00:12:52,540
Your child is fine.

231
00:12:52,666 --> 00:12:53,470
You're pregnant.

232
00:12:55,660 --> 00:12:57,430
Then why couldn't you
feel anything just now?

233
00:13:00,350 --> 00:13:01,990
Judging from the look on your face,

234
00:13:02,140 --> 00:13:03,660
you are carrying twins.

235
00:13:04,088 --> 00:13:05,070
Just now, I was feeling

236
00:13:05,110 --> 00:13:06,590
the pulse of the other baby.

237
00:13:07,310 --> 00:13:08,260
Twins?

238
00:13:10,470 --> 00:13:12,266
Your Highness,
is what you said really true?

239
00:13:13,780 --> 00:13:14,260
Yes, it is.

240
00:13:15,488 --> 00:13:16,777
Imperial Physician Liu,

241
00:13:16,866 --> 00:13:18,666
is Princess Consort Jin
telling the truth?

242
00:13:20,780 --> 00:13:21,350
Your Majesty,

243
00:13:22,020 --> 00:13:24,500
please forgive my lack of skill.

244
00:13:25,110 --> 00:13:27,470
It's too early in the pregnancy

245
00:13:28,020 --> 00:13:29,590
to make a clear diagnosis.

246
00:13:39,444 --> 00:13:40,488
Imperial Physician Liu,

247
00:13:40,622 --> 00:13:41,777
she passed all three rounds.

248
00:13:41,844 --> 00:13:42,888
What do you think?

249
00:13:43,222 --> 00:13:43,933
Well...

250
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:45,190
Even after the three tests,

251
00:13:45,620 --> 00:13:48,020
her true abilities remain unproven.

252
00:13:48,900 --> 00:13:50,190
Letting her pass just like that

253
00:13:51,020 --> 00:13:52,350
is rather unjustified.

254
00:13:53,780 --> 00:13:55,020
Aliya is from Xilin.

255
00:13:55,310 --> 00:13:56,190
Their medical practice

256
00:13:56,190 --> 00:13:57,490
is naturally different from ours.

257
00:13:58,020 --> 00:13:59,430
I ask you to reconsider, Father.

258
00:14:00,140 --> 00:14:02,110
I have sought treatment
for my legs for years

259
00:14:02,140 --> 00:14:02,990
without success.

260
00:14:03,540 --> 00:14:05,020
Now, under Aliya's care,

261
00:14:05,350 --> 00:14:06,500
there's finally progress.

262
00:14:07,230 --> 00:14:08,740
I don't want to give up now.

263
00:14:09,950 --> 00:14:10,350
Father,

264
00:14:11,020 --> 00:14:13,190
if I could cure
Noble Consort's chronic illness,

265
00:14:14,380 --> 00:14:15,230
then I believe

266
00:14:15,310 --> 00:14:16,844
I can heal His Highness's legs too.

267
00:14:20,244 --> 00:14:21,288
Noble Consort.

268
00:14:22,622 --> 00:14:24,860
Did Princess Consort Jin
treat your chronic illness?

269
00:14:25,860 --> 00:14:26,900
Actually...

270
00:14:29,110 --> 00:14:29,860
Actually, Mother

271
00:14:30,230 --> 00:14:31,310
was cured of her condition

272
00:14:31,333 --> 00:14:33,110
thanks to Princess Consort Jin's treatment.

273
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:35,533
Greetings, Father.

274
00:14:38,577 --> 00:14:39,430
Noble Consort,

275
00:14:40,470 --> 00:14:42,140
is what Yunnuo said true?

276
00:14:50,950 --> 00:14:51,590
It's true.

277
00:14:54,133 --> 00:14:56,140
Noble Consort's illness
had resisted all treatment.

278
00:14:57,288 --> 00:14:58,400
Princess Consort Jin,

279
