Well, do you feel anything?

568
00:29:41,260 --> 00:29:42,150
What?

569
00:29:43,710 --> 00:29:45,260
I mean the effects of hypnosis.

570
00:29:47,740 --> 00:29:50,540
I've had a nice nap.
Now I feel quite good.

571
00:29:51,950 --> 00:29:52,780
Wait, don't...

572
00:29:53,230 --> 00:29:55,670
Don't you feel anything else?

573
00:29:57,820 --> 00:29:58,190
I do.

574
00:29:59,230 --> 00:30:02,430
I feel quite dizzy from your shaking.

575
00:30:06,950 --> 00:30:07,430
I'm doomed.

576
00:30:08,150 --> 00:30:09,190
This time I'm done for.

577
00:30:10,820 --> 00:30:11,430
Aliya.

578
00:30:11,710 --> 00:30:12,740
Don't lose hope.

579
00:30:13,300 --> 00:30:15,060
You can keep hypnotizing me.

580
00:30:15,390 --> 00:30:17,390
I really did have a nice nap just now.

581
00:30:17,740 --> 00:30:17,990
Go on.

582
00:30:21,400 --> 00:30:22,422
Your Highness.

583
00:30:23,020 --> 00:30:24,260
If you're enjoying this,

584
00:30:25,060 --> 00:30:26,260
I'll do as you wish, then.

585
00:30:59,260 --> 00:31:00,870
You... You're standing!

586
00:31:04,470 --> 00:31:05,580
Yuetao!

587
00:31:05,950 --> 00:31:06,540
Hurry!

588
00:31:06,910 --> 00:31:07,500
Your Highness!

589
00:31:07,580 --> 00:31:08,300
Your Highness!

590
00:31:08,300 --> 00:31:09,622
- I'm feeling weak...
- Quick!

591
00:31:14,780 --> 00:31:15,820
Your legs are healed!

592
00:31:15,870 --> 00:31:16,950
You just stood up!

593
00:31:17,100 --> 00:31:18,910
I tried really hard to stand up,

594
00:31:19,230 --> 00:31:21,630
but then my legs gave out again.

595
00:31:21,950 --> 00:31:24,020
Now I can't feel anything.

596
00:31:29,100 --> 00:31:30,630
How useless I am.

597
00:31:31,630 --> 00:31:32,670
I can't heal you.

598
00:31:33,260 --> 00:31:33,740
Aliya.

599
00:31:34,500 --> 00:31:35,430
Don't be discouraged.

600
00:31:36,390 --> 00:31:37,500
I'll stand again one day.

601
00:31:53,100 --> 00:31:54,630
If I can never walk again,

602
00:31:56,540 --> 00:31:57,390
will you stay with me?

603
00:32:05,888 --> 00:32:07,355
You're blessed, Your Highness.

604
00:32:07,500 --> 00:32:08,630
You'll surely recover.

605
00:32:10,260 --> 00:32:11,430
So, will you stay with me

606
00:32:11,780 --> 00:32:12,340
or not?

607
00:32:14,911 --> 00:32:15,577
I will.

608
00:32:16,780 --> 00:32:17,820
I will definitely heal you.

609
00:32:25,150 --> 00:32:26,150
You clearly fancy me,

610
00:32:26,511 --> 00:32:27,800
but you just won't admit it.

611
00:32:28,950 --> 00:32:29,670
This woman.

612
00:32:44,390 --> 00:32:44,820
Guihu.

613
00:32:45,755 --> 00:32:46,950
Why are you standing there?

614
00:32:47,430 --> 00:32:48,020
Get over here.

615
00:32:52,850 --> 00:32:55,280
I told you to send the invitation
to Prince Jin's Residence.

616
00:32:55,288 --> 00:32:56,577
Why are you back here already?

617
00:32:58,155 --> 00:32:59,044
Your Highness.

618
00:32:59,200 --> 00:33:01,333
Princess Consort Jin
isn't worthy of dining with you.

619
00:33:02,333 --> 00:33:03,430
What do you mean by that?

620
00:33:08,060 --> 00:33:08,780
In broad daylight,

621
00:33:08,844 --> 00:33:10,466
Prince Jin and Princess Consort Jin

622
00:33:10,466 --> 00:33:11,777
were being indecent in public!

623
00:33:11,800 --> 00:33:12,466
What?

624
00:33:12,470 --> 00:33:12,740
They...

625
00:33:18,390 --> 00:33:22,133
Maybe they were doing
some sort of treatment.

626
00:33:22,990 --> 00:33:24,260
But that didn't look like one.

627
00:33:24,580 --> 00:33:25,300
Enough, Guihu.

628
00:33:26,422 --> 00:33:27,377
Keep an eye on them.

629
00:33:28,355 --> 00:33:30,111
Whether it's the Prince Jin's Residence

630
00:33:30,111 --> 00:33:31,377
or Everything Guild,

631
00:33:31,540 --> 00:33:32,866
don't let your guard down.

632
00:33:33,155 --> 00:33:34,244
Yes, Your Highness.

633
00:34:13,685 --> 00:34:18,045
♪The clouds stretch endlessly
across the sky♪

634
00:34:20,885 --> 00:34:25,285
♪Looking down at eyes
that gaze into the distance♪

635
00:34:26,845 --> 00:34:30,015
♪Time keeps moving on♪

636
00:34:30,635 --> 00:34:33,195
♪Whose footprints are left behind?♪

637
00:34:33,595 --> 00:34:40,055
♪It's more than
just the courage to yearn♪

638
00:34:41,685 --> 00:34:44,495
♪It's destined that we cannot be close♪

639
00:34:45,335 --> 00:34:48,415
♪Loving you is a secret♪

640
00:34:48,955 --> 00:34:51,615
♪Afraid of disturbing you
and then you'd distance yourself♪

641
00:34:51,615 --> 00:34:54,955
♪Endlessly♪

642
00:34:56,035 --> 00:34:59,485
♪How I wish I could dive into the sea♪

643
00:34:59,865 --> 00:35:02,485
♪And gently rest♪

644
00:35:02,485 --> 00:35:09,445
♪It's to soothe the reason
for your heart's pain♪

645
00:35:09,815 --> 00:35:14,095
♪If everything could overcome
all barriers and fall in love♪

646
00:35:14,445 --> 00:35:16,965
♪Even the cloud and sea
could be together♪

647
00:35:17,175 --> 00:35:20,375
♪Forget how far from shore
and how dangerous it is♪

648
00:35:20,625 --> 00:35:24,265
♪We can't see♪

649
00:35:24,475 --> 00:35:28,805
♪If distance can't tear us apart
and it's not hard to endure♪

650
00:35:28,805 --> 00:35:31,555
♪Our tears will stay together♪

651
00:35:31,805 --> 00:35:37,445
♪Don’t forget the love♪

652
00:35:39,065 --> 00:35:42,435
♪They could never have♪
